Reading each part should be separated with one new line. Resources used in player has to be same as in global resources,
same for the units.

Global resources -> comma separated strings
example: Bricks,Weapons,Crystals

Global Units -> comma separated strings
example:Builders,Soldiers,Magicians

Card definitions -> Name as string, Resource from global resources, amount as int (minus value would give u resources)
                 -> |attack number, defense number|effect type, power (if needed), resource(if needed);,
                 -> card definitions can end with empty line or indent and then empty line

example:AntWarrior,Weapons,20|5,0|b,10
example:Dragon,Weapons,10,Crystals,10|20,0|b,-30
example:AssaultRifle,Weapons,20|3,0|b,-5
example:Archer,Weapons,25|6,0|b,-15
example:Wagon,Bricks,10|5,5|b,+10,b,-10
example:Burglar,Weapons,15,Crystals,10|10,10|b,20,b,-20
example:AntBuilder,Bricks,7|0,3|b,20
example:Tower,Bricks,10|0,5|b,10
example:Fortress,Bricks,20|0,7|b,20
example:CrystalGenerator,Crystals,5|5,5|r,20,Crystals
example:BrickGenerator,Crystals,5|2,5|r,20,Bricks
example:WeaponsGenerator,Crystals,5|5,0|r,20,Weapons
example:CrystalDestroyer,Crystals,5|5,0|r,-10,Crystals
example:School,Bricks,5,Crystals,5|0,6|u,4,Builders
example:Army,Weapons,5,Crystals,5|5,0|u,4,Soldiers
example:DavidCopperfield,Crystals,10|7,7|u,4,Magicians
example:ResourceMine,Crystals,20|0,10|r,10,Bricks;,r,10,Crystals;,r,10,Weapons
example:MagicTrick,Crystals,5|5,5|s
example:Refiller,Crystals,10|0,6|f,2
example:CrystalStealer,Crystals,5|6,0|r,10,Crystals;,r,-10,Crystals

special_example:  UltimateCard,Crystals,10|0,6|f,2,r,10,Crystals;,r,-10,Crystals;,r,10,Bricks;,r,10,Crystals;,r,10,Weapons;,b,20,b,-20


Player's name as a string
example:Pepa

Indexes into global Card deck
example:1,2,3,2,1,4

Base values
example:40,0,100

Refill map -> which units refill which resources from global resources and units
example:Bricks,Builders
example:Weapons,Soldiers
example:Crystals,Magicians

Resources and amount of resources from global resources
example:Bricks,50
example:Weapons,50
example:Crystals,50

Units and amount of units from global units
example:Builders,4
example:Magicians,4
example:Soldiers,4

Second player same as the first one
Honza

